title: The Faxmonkey Files - World of Warcraft Video Soundtrack
description:
I've always loved the music Faxmonkey uses in his World of Warcraft videos so I made it my mission to gather the tracks from around the web.  From his first video Monkeys Gone Wild to WTFrost Vol.2; Faxmonkey has used a total of 78 tracks, all of which are included in this torrent! Unfortunately, as all these tracks are from different sources there is no constant bitrate - it varies track to track; but I've tried to get the highest quality version possible.

Listed alphabetically by the video they were featured in and then by order of appearance; the tracks are as follows:
